<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink395">
<l>muḷivayirp piṟanta vaḷivaḷar kūreric</l>
<l>cuṭarviṭu neṭuṅkoṭi viṭarmukai muḻaṅku</l>
<l>miṉṉā varuñcuran tīrntaṉa meṉmela</l>
<l>vēkumati vāḻiyō kuṟumakaḷ pōtukalantu</l>
<l>kaṟaṅkicai yaruvi vīḻum</l>
<l>piṟaṅkiruñ cōlainam malaikeḻu nāṭṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>We have crossed the harsh unpleasant desert,  </l>
<l>where great flames, born in the dry bamboo and growing in the wind, </l>
<l>glitter in mountain clefts and caves, like long banners that produce shining!  </l>
<l>May you live long, little daughter! </l>
<l>Walk very slowly through our mountainous country, where in the glistening vast groves </l>
<l>waterfalls cascade down with loud noise, bringing flowers. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
